c: 3
v: 187
t: "Futhi (khumbulani) ngesikhathi uMvelinqangi amukela isivumelwano kulabo ababenikezwa incwadi ukuze bayichazele abantu ngokusobala futhi bangayifihli kodwa bona bayintshinga ngemuva kwemihlane yabo, futhi bathenga ngayo okungeyinzuzo yalutho ngempela kubi kakhulu lokho abakuthengileyo"